WEBVTT

00:00:27.917 --> 00:00:30.518
and I'm also the mother
of two little girls.

00:00:30.542 --> 00:00:35.018
And I started to become interested
in this question in 2015

00:00:35.042 --> 00:00:37.768
when I suddenly realized
that there were vast --

00:00:37.792 --> 00:00:40.809
almost unimaginable amounts of data traces

00:00:40.833 --> 00:00:44.000
that are being produced
and collected about children.

00:00:44.792 --> 00:00:46.768
So I launched a research project,

00:00:46.792 --> 00:00:49.268
which is called Child Data Citizen,

00:00:49.292 --> 00:00:51.417
and I aimed at filling in the blank.

00:00:52.583 --> 00:00:55.601
Now you may think
that I'm here to blame you

00:00:55.625 --> 00:00:58.393
for posting photos
of your children on social media,

00:00:58.417 --> 00:01:00.559
but that's not really the point.